Package: gsEstimators
Type: Package
Title: Group Sequential Estimators for Clinical Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Joseph", "Caldwell", email = "jcald447@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Oliver", "Chi", email = "o.chi1@lancaster.ac.uk", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides functions to calculate various estimators 
    (MLE, UMVUE, UBC-MLE, cMUE, etc.) for group sequential 
    designs in clinical trials. Includes simulation support 
    and tools for operating characteristics.
